                <p>Magic prayer accompanied by a praxis for the protection of goods. The prayer uses ʾasmāt, which are certainly derived from
                    Arabic Islamic phrases and terms as e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ar">bi-smi-llāh</foreign>, 
                    <foreign xml:lang="ar">ar-rāḥmatu-llāh</foreign> or <foreign xml:lang="ar">ʾAllāh-hummā</foreign>.</p>
